<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Nos mudamos a Estudia CEST</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;700&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --ink: #0f172a;
      --muted: #475569;
      --line: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
      --paper: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      --brand: #0f766e;
      --brand-strong: #115e59;
      --accent: #ea580c;
      --brand-soft: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.16);
      --shadow: 0 28px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html,
    body {
      min-height: 100%;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Source Sans 3', system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.24), transparent 34%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.24), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #f5efe6 0%, #dff4ef 48%, #f9fafb 100%);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .shell {
      width: min(760px, 100%);
      background: var(--paper);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 28px 28px 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--brand-strong);
      background: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.16);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
    }

    .eyebrow::before {
      content: "";
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--brand);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.12);
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.35rem);
      line-height: 0.96;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      margin-top: 18px;
      max-width: 12ch;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin-top: 16px;
      max-width: 44ch;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .badge {
      min-width: 150px;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62));
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .badge-label {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .badge-value {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--accent);
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 12px 28px 30px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .notice {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .notice strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .notice p {
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .details {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .detail-card {
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 18px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    .detail-card span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .detail-card p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--ink);
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-height: 54px;
      padding: 0 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 0.16s ease, box-shadow 0.16s ease, background 0.16s ease;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand-strong));
      box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.22);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      color: var(--ink);
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .footnote {
      font-size: 0.96rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .footnote a {
      color: var(--brand-strong);
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      body {
        padding: 16px;
      }

      .hero,
      .content {
        padding-left: 20px;
        padding-right: 20px;
      }

      .badge {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="shell">
    <section class="hero">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Acceso bloqueado en este dominio</span>
        <h1>La plataforma de estudiantes se mudó.</h1>
        <p>El acceso desde <strong>profefranciscopancho.com/estudiantes</strong> fue deshabilitado para evitar ingresos al dominio antiguo. Desde aquí no se abrirá automáticamente el panel nuevo.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="badge" aria-label="Cambio de acceso">
        <div class="badge-label">Acción requerida</div>
        <div class="badge-value">Continuar manualmente</div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="content">
      <div class="notice">
        <strong>Nuevo acceso oficial</strong>
        <p>Para entrar al nuevo dominio debes pulsar el botón. Esto evita que una sesión activa en <strong>www.estudiacest.com</strong> salte este aviso automáticamente.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="details">
        <article class="detail-card">
          <span>Dominio anterior</span>
          <p>profefranciscopancho.com/estudiantes</p>
        </article>
        <article class="detail-card">
          <span>Dominio actual</span>
          <p>www.estudiacest.com</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://www.estudiacest.com">Ir ahora a www.estudiacest.com</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://www.estudiacest.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Abrir en una pestaña nueva</a>
      </div>

      <p class="footnote">Si tenías este enlace guardado, actualízalo al nuevo dominio. Para ingresar a lecturas, perfil o panel, usa siempre <a href="https://www.estudiacest.com">www.estudiacest.com</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>